# ⚙️ COA Concept 3: Edge Computing

🔥 Modern cloud + IoT topic.

---

## 1️⃣ Simple Idea

Instead of processing data far away in cloud:

👉 process near data source.

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Local grocery store vs distant warehouse.

Local response faster.

---

## Examples

* self-driving cars
* smart cameras
* IoT devices

---

## Why Important?

✔ lower latency
✔ faster response
✔ less bandwidth usage

---

## 🔗 Connection

Useful in:

* AI inference
* real-time systems

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why edge computing reduces latency?**

👉 Because computation happens closer to data source.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="8n2qpl"
Edge = compute near user/device
```

